p= `Hi admin, ${buyer.firstName || ''} ${buyer.lastName || ''} just made a purchase below are the order details`
h3 Order Details
table(border=1)
    tr
        th Order Number
        td #{order._id}
    tr
        th Total Quantities
        td #{order.quantity}
    tr
        th Product Details
        td
            table(border=0)
                thead
                tr
                    th Product Name
                    th Quantity
                    th Unit Price
                    th Unit Subtotal
                tbody
                    tr
                        td #{order.product.name}
                        td #{order.quantity}
                        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment/order.quantity}
                        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment}

    tr
        th Subtotal
        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment}

h4 Take Action
p Your action is needed for this order<br/> APPROVE : <a href="#{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{approvalToken}/#{admin._id}/approved"> #{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{approvalToken}/#{admin._id}/approved</a><br/>
